data.description: MOVE IN READY!  Deltona Lakes, in Volusia County’s best kept secret communities, a highly desired neighborhood.  When you enter this 1,714 sq ft beautiful one-story vaulted ceiling home, you are astonished with the available space it has to offer.  The home’s skylight and windows bring in an abundance of natural light and multiple sliders providing amazing views of the outdoor screened in patio and yard.  The family room also flows into the kitchen, formal dining room, and the formal living room with a wood burning fireplace, making this the perfect space for entertaining!  The master bedroom with a closet and a master bath with a custom tiled shower.  On the other side of this spacious split-floor plan home, are two bedrooms with closets and a hall bathroom.  This home features tile floors, a privacy vinyl fence (permit available), a Nest doorbell and a Nest thermostat.  In addition, a laundry room, two car garage, newer roof 2020 (permit available), HVAC 13yoa, and Water heater 11yoa.  NO HOA!  This community attends Volusia County finest schools, convenient to local Hospitals, markets, located in Central Florida, near restaurants, shops, I4 and major roadways to beaches, attractions, Historic Sanford and Downtown Orlando.  This is a great opportunity to make this home your own.
